camPrepareFov 
Game: Armed Assault (1.00) 
Description: Prepares the camera field of view (zoom). The default zoom level 
 is 0.7, 0.01 is the nearest and 2 the furthest zoom value. The angle 
 of the field of view is atan(FOV)*2 radians when in 4:3 aspect ratio 
. Needs the call of camCommitPrepared to be conducted.  
Syntax:  
 camera camPrepareFov fieldOfView 
Parameters: 
camera: Object 
fieldOfView: Number 
Return Value: 
 Nothing